### ============================================================
### MITRA JOB APPLICATIONS API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
### Data seeder yang tersedia:
### - mitra.company.a@kompeta.test → punya vacancy: accounting-staff-1602be (id=1), security-freelance-jakarta (id=2)
###   → menerima lamaran dari Budi Santoso (NISN 0001234567) untuk Accounting Staff
### - mitra.company.b@kompeta.test → punya vacancy: data-entry-operator-bandung (id=3), junior-qa-tester-remote (id=4)
###   → menerima lamaran dari Ahmad Wijaya (NISN 0002345678) untuk Data Entry Operator
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Login mitra perusahaan (PT Binajasa Sumber Sarana)
# @name loginMitra
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "mitra",
  "email": "mitra.company.a@kompeta.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ============================================================
### 1) LIST LAMARAN MASUK (semua)
### Endpoint: GET /api/mitra/job-applications
### ============================================================

# @name listApplications
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginMitra.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 2) LIST LAMARAN MASUK - DENGAN PAGINATION
### ============================================================

# @name listApplicationsPaginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications?page=1&per_page=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginMitra.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 3) LIST LAMARAN MASUK - FILTER BY JOB VACANCY
### Vacancy id=1 = accounting-staff-1602be (milik mitra.company.a)
### ============================================================

# @name listApplicationsByVacancy
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications?job_vacancy_id=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginMitra.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 4) DETAIL LAMARAN
### Endpoint: GET /api/mitra/job-applications/{id}
### Gunakan ID dari response list (#1): listApplications.response.body.$.data[0].id
### ============================================================

@applicationId = {{listApplications.response.body.$.data[0].id}}

# @name showApplication
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications/{{applicationId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginMitra.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 5) DOWNLOAD CV PELAMAR
### Endpoint: GET /api/mitra/job-applications/{id}/cv
### ============================================================

# @name downloadCv
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications/{{applicationId}}/cv
Accept: application/octet-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{loginMitra.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 6) AKSES TANPA AUTH (expect 401)
### ============================================================

# @name noAuthTest
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra/job-applications
Accept: application/json
